  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The next day, the door was open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Open the door.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They camed in, [INAUDIBLE] with this, with this [INAUDIBLE], certain other with the list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], [NON-ENGLISH], [LAUGHS] [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], Gabriel [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Wolfovich ?] Krause, stand up!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stand up, [LAUGHS] and the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mean go, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stand up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't have time to tell him goodbye, and I [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I open the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I go with these-- these people-- with these two.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One in the front of me, [LAUGHS] [? one with the other. ?] And I go out, and so what was the luck?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was not a [? first ?] officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's why they let you out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't an ?] officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He tell me-- he give me prognosis that I supposed to go out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I go out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember to this day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I go out, and from this moment, some other story start.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these officers, because was ready to find out, they killed 12,000 to 15,000 Polish officers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put them in all kind of-- all kind of places like [INAUDIBLE] Polish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean like-- like the Germans make special places for this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They keep these officers, and they start in 1941-- and I forget the date.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they got a treaty-- Poland got a treaty with Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, not Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean Russia, with the German got a treaty for 20 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all of a sudden one day, they start a war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this all Polish officer was concentrated in-- in Ukraine, some places on the borders, and it came a special [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This mean a-- a special-- special thing for Stalin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] Polish lagers.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
